>So how do you create captivating visual content that attracts, engages, and retains your audience? In this post, I&#8217;m going to equip you to do just that. I&#8217;m going to cover:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Exactly what visual marketing is,<\/li>\n<li>Five stellar tools to help you create designer-worthy content, and<\/li>\n<li>Tips to make sure your images meet your technical optimization standards.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>So first, let&#8217;s cover the basics of visual marketing.<\/p>\n<h2>What is visual marketing?<\/h2>\n<p>Because the competition for consumers&#8217;\u00a0attention is fierce,\u00a0brands embrace the\u00a0power of visuals to grab viewers&#8217; attention\u00a0and engage their audience.\u00a0Visual marketing\u00a0means\u00a0using graphics,\u00a0videos, infographics, apps, GIFs,\u00a0memes,\u00a0SlideShare presentations,\u00a0animations,\u00a0sketches, doodles,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2014\/04\/28\/user-generated-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">user-generated content<\/a>,\u00a0and\u00a0<a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2016\/09\/29\/data-visualization-tools\">data visualization<\/a> to educate or get a\u00a0message across.<\/p>\n<p>We have all heard that\u00a0a\u00a0&#8220;picture is worth a thousand words.&#8221;\u00a0In the digital marketing landscape, pictures and other visual content forms are also worth more impressions and higher conversion rates.<\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4>We have all heard that\u00a0a\u00a0&#8220;picture is worth a thousand words.&#8221;\u00a0In the digital marketing landscape, pictures and other visual content forms are also worth more impressions and higher conversion rates.<\/h4>\n<\/blockquote>\n<h2>Why is visual marketing important?<\/h2>\n<p>When you are scrolling through your\u00a0social media feeds, what type of content grabs your attention? Chances\u00a0are it is some type of\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2017\/03\/24\/best-instagram-marketing-campaigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">engaging visual content.<\/a>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Social media\u00a0visual\u00a0content evokes an emotional reaction for viewers. It also\u00a0yields the most engagement and best return on investment.<\/p>\n<p>Since\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.t-sciences.com\/news\/humans-process-visual-data-better\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">90% of the information our brains process is visual<\/a>, it is crucial for your business to focus on creating engaging visual content to attract your target audience.\u00a0Do you need more convincing on the value of visual content marketing?<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.forbes.com\/sites\/forbestechcouncil\/2018\/04\/02\/visual-content-the-future-of-storytelling\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">91% of people<\/a>\u00a0prefer visual over written content<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hubspot.com\/state-of-marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">70% of businesses<\/a>\u00a0invest money in content marketing,\u00a0including visual marketing.<\/li>\n<li>According to\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/contentmarketinginstitute.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/12\/2019_B2C_Research-FINAL-PDF-12_10_18.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Content Marketing Institute&#8217;s 2019\u00a0 Benchmarks, Budgets, and Trends<\/a>, the majority of B2C marketers are increasing how much they spend on visual content.<\/li>\n<li>In a 2020 Digital Marketing Skills Survey,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/research\/digital-skills-survey-2020-results\/marketing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BrainStation cites 67% of respondents<\/a>\u00a0listed Instagram, an entirely visual platform, as an effective social media marketing platform.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Visual marketing tools to engage your audience and boost your ROI<\/h2>\n<p>As we just established, using engaging visuals on your social media channels can result in huge returns. With the right tools, creating visuals is an achievable task, even for those who are not professional graphic designers or videographers.\u00a0\u00a0Below are five of my favorite visual marketing tools and how to use them to create imagery and tell your brand story to connect with your customers.<\/p>\n<h2>1. Bannersnack<\/h2>\n<p>If you are looking to create social media visuals and display banner ads,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bannersnack.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bannersnack<\/a>\u00a0is an excellent tool for you.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"f65c495e-654b-4941-b51b-d51e7538c00a\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20bannersnack20banner20maker.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools bannersnack banner maker\" width=\"800\" height=\"328\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p>It is web-based,\u00a0which means there is no need to download or install any software.\u00a0Choose from a wide variety of editable templates\u00a0for<a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2019\/03\/19\/social-media-for-small-business\"> all major social media platforms<\/a> or start from scratch.<\/p>\n<h3>How to create a banner set from a Bannersnack template<\/h3>\n<p>Select the banner size you want to create from one of the many presets\u00a0Bannersnack\u00a0offers for most of the\u00a0popular\u00a0social media and ad banner sizes.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"4c625db9-0da0-42a4-b568-7f6db178ac90\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20bannersnack202.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools banne