ory.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"385\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<h2>3. Venngage<\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2011\/05\/26\/infographic-marketing-interview\">Infographics<\/a>\u00a0show data, statistics, and processes in memorable and visually appealing designs.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/venngage.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Venngage<\/a>\u00a0enables users to create infographics in three easy steps:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose from one of the professionally designed templates.<\/li>\n<li>Add charts, text, and information to visualize your data.<\/li>\n<li>Customize your design by changing the colors, fonts, images, and other elements.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>The free version allows you to create five different\u00a0infographics\u00a0to see how you like the program.\u00a0Venngage\u00a0gives users\u00a0access to an extensive database of thematic designs, stock images, icons, charts, and templates.<\/p>\n<p>If you want to open more features and create more than five infographics, you will need to upgrade to a\u00a0premium\u00a0version.<\/p>\n<p>Start by\u00a0registering for a free account.\u00a0Log into the dashboard\u00a0to\u00a0create\u00a0a new design and see any infographics you have already created.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"751b014f-5d92-4312-8c1c-b66f24e0bb15\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20venngage.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools venngage\" width=\"800\" height=\"383\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p>To get started\u00a0creating an infographic, click on the green circle with the plus sign inside\u00a0it.\u00a0Select Free from the dropdown menu, search by keyword, topic, or feature, or scroll through the options to find a template you want to customize.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"b05b2dcf-be1e-4150-9483-9ed3751cccc8\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20venngage20templates.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools venngage templates\" width=\"800\" height=\"330\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<h3>How to visualize your data with\u00a0Venngage<\/h3>\n<p>Importing your\u00a0valuable\u00a0data into an organized and visually appealing chart makes it easier to digest and understand.<\/p>\n<p>With\u00a0Venngage, start by selecting the type of chart you want to use,\u00a0including:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pie charts<\/li>\n<li>Bubble charts<\/li>\n<li>Bar charts<\/li>\n<li>Pictographs<\/li>\n<li>Line charts<\/li>\n<li>Word clouds<\/li>\n<li>Stacked bar charts<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Type, copy and paste, or import your data in a CSV or XLSX format. Your data will instantly fill the chart.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"a322de0f-57b8-4cf3-b9e6-90eea3e94e53\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20venngage20example.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools venngage example\" width=\"800\" height=\"475\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<h3>How to customize a template with Venngage<\/h3>\n<p>Venngage\u00a0uses a drop and drag editor that makes it simple to customize a template. Edit and <a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2017\/02\/06\/personalized-marketing\">personalize<\/a> it by changing the fonts, text, visuals, colors, and charts to match your brand and messaging.<\/p>\n<p>Drag widgets onto your canvas and customize their orientation, color, and size. You\u00a0can also lock groups into place. Enhance your designs with images and icons from the built-in library or upload your own.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"ed4edc9a-9883-44fb-ac66-41d2ba6af47c\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/visual20marketing20tools20customize20template.png\" alt=\"visual marketing tools customize template\" width=\"800\" height=\"436\" \/><\/div>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"text-align-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><a href=\"\/\/newhorizons123.com\/venngage-engaging-infographics\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Image source<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n<h3>Why use templates?<\/h3>\n<p>Templates make it easy to swap out elements such as text, images, charts, tables, and graphs with your own.\u00a0An example of templates&#8217; power\u00a0is the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/hostingdata.co.uk\/squarespace-review\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">popularity of website builders such as Squarespace<\/a>\u00a0to <a href=\"\/blog\/ws\/2019\/12\/31\/basic-website\">create professional-looking websites<\/a> for people with no design or coding experience.\u00a0For marketers who are not graphic designers, creating attractive infographics from scratch is a challenge.\u00a0Customizing a template enables users to produce and share professional-looking designs to their audience, such as the\u00a0example\u00a0below.<\/p>\n<div class=\"embedded-entity align-center\" data-embed-button=\"images\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:media.simple_image\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"5dac5b55-de9e-478d-bc2c-de3928dcac16\" data-langcode=\"en\">\n<article>\n<div><img decoding=